{"word":"Pillow","slug":"pillow","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Pillow</b> 1. A cushion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=28&verse=11'>Gen 28:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=28&verse=18'>Gen 28:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=26&verse=7'>1Sa 26:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=26&verse=11'>1Sa 26:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=26&verse=16'>1Sa 26:16</a><br/> 2. A support for the head:<br/> - Stones used for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=28&verse=11'>Gen 28:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=28&verse=18'>Gen 28:18</a> <br/> - Called Bolster<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=26&verse=7'>1Sa 26:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=26&verse=12'>1Sa 26:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=26&verse=16'>1Sa 26:16</a> <br/> - Made of goats' hair<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=19&verse=13'>1Sa 19:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=19&verse=16'>1Sa 19:16</a> <br/> - Jesus sleeps on<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=4&verse=38'>Mar 4:38</a> <br/> Figurative, of false teachers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=13&verse=18'>Eze 13:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=13&verse=20'>Eze 13:20</a>"}]}